Package com.ulflander.minethat.model

This classes are the internal model of document, tokens and so on in Minethat java services.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Storable Models that get dedicated mongo table must implement this interface.
 

Class Summary
Chapter A chapter contains paragraphs and is contained into a document.
Document Document is the main model in processing.
Edge Edge is a relationship between a document and another resource.
Entity An entity.
Heading Heading is a special paragraph that contains only a few words.
Job A job holds information about documents to be processed, processors to run on them or presets of processors to use, and also about the customer that initiated the job.
JobProcessor A Processor representation as for a job.
JobProcessorOption Options for a processor.
ListItem ListItem is an extended paragraph that represent a list item.
Meta Meta informations about a document.
Paragraph A paragraph contains sentences and is contained into chapters.
Sentence Model of sentence.
Text Text is the base class for any text model: document, paragraph, token...
TextLength Lenght indicator of a text.
Token A token is the most tiny part of a document: a word, a number, and so on.
 

Enum Summary
DocumentStatus State of processing document.
HeadingLevel Defines level of a heading.
JobDocumentType Job document type - defines what value of JobDocument is: a file, an URL, a raw string...
JobGateway List of available job gateways.
JobStatus Status for job executions.
Language Represents a language in Minethat model.
TokenType Represents the type of a token.
 

Package com.ulflander.minethat.model Description

This classes are the internal model of document, tokens and so on in Minethat java services.
